						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the house of Nallappa.</p>						

						<p>SADĀŚIVADĒVARĀYA.</p>						

						<p>1547 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka year 1469, Plavaṅga Āśvija śu. 11 (Thursday) corresponding to September 29, 1547 A.D.</p>						

						<p>Mutilated and incomplete. Refers to some gifts of land situated at Pedirūru in thaṇḍikoṭasīma, made by <hi rend="italic">Mahānāyaṁkachāryya</hi> Kūnapuli Dāvināyani Pedapāpi Nāyanīṁyāru.</p>						

						</summary>
